Localization.Name: Li-Tok Boots Dark Green
Localization.Description: Stylish yet rugged, NorthStar's Li-Tok boots are made from a composite nylon fabric, vulcanized rubber grips that hold fast to a variety of surfaces, and reinforced ankle support making these perfect for hanging out or on the job.\n\nWomen's sizes currently out of stock.
